1. Danas sam oborio* rekord* u trčanju. (Today I broke* the record* in running.)
2. Taj sportista drži svetski rekord* u bacanju koplja. (That athlete holds the world record* in javelin throwing.)
3. Rekordna* poseta je došla na koncert. (A record-breaking* attendance came to the concert.)
4. Rekorderka* je bila veoma ponosna na svoj uspeh. (The record holder* was very proud of her achievement.)
5. Ovaj album oborio* je sve rekorde* prodaje. (This album broke* all sales records*.)
6. Pokušaćemo da postavimo novi rekord* u skoku u vis. (We will try to set a new record* in high jump.)
7. Rekordni* dug je teško vratiti. (A record debt is difficult to repay.)
8. Naša firma je postigla rekordne* prihode prošle godine. (Our company achieved record revenues last year.)
9. Ovaj grad ima najviše rekordnih* temperatura u letnjem periodu. (This city has the highest record temperatures in the summer period.)
10. Treba nam dobar plan da oborimo* taj rekord* u plivanju. (We need a good plan to break* that record* in swimming.)